<p>You will use your strong communication and project management skills to work closely with stakeholders, designers and developers. It is your responsibility to accompany a project from start to finish. To help define project goals you use your understanding of business as well as user requirements. You will also use your background in web design and development to ensure feasibility and creative excellence.</p>

